      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'm looking for a smooth sale, so I've priced it to move. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
