    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp via six individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the critical 'Big Three' already addressed: a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with VAC coated bearings, and a reinforced rear subframe. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory M-variable differential lock. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis dynamics are as sharp as the day it left Regensburg. Zero deferred maintenance; purely an enthusiast-grade investment.",
